on Seeking Alpha, at least judging by the number of conversations these articles tend to associate with. My </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1675930162/image_1675930162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741758-janux-therapeutics-hype-breeds-volatility-and-that-should-give-you-pause", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 17:35:27"}, {"id": "4741629", "title": "Amazon: A Compelling Buying Opportunity", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311461417/image_1311461417.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Amazon warehouse facility in Houston, TX.\" data-id=\"1311461417\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"962px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311461417/image_1311461417.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311461417/image_1311461417.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311461417/image_1311461417.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311461417/image_1311461417.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311461417/image_1311461417.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311461417/image_1311461417.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311461417/image_1311461417.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311461417/image_1311461417.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Brett_Hondow</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>My thesis</h2> <p>Amazon (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMZN\" title=\"Amazon.com, Inc.\">AMZN</a></span>) aggressively drives innovation to remain at the forefront of the thriving cloud industry, which experiences solid AI tailwinds. Numerous new offerings and initiatives were rolled out by the company over the next few months. The latest quarterly financial</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1311461417/image_1311461417.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741629-amazon-a-compelling-buying-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 17:30:00"}, {"id": "4741745", "title": "ADT Inc: I Have More Confidence That Growth Can Accelerate", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638690525/image_638690525.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Security guard using digital tablet in security control room with video wall\" data-id=\"638690525\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638690525/image_638690525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638690525/image_638690525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638690525/image_638690525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638690525/image_638690525.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638690525/image_638690525.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638690525/image_638690525.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638690525/image_638690525.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638690525/image_638690525.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment overview</h2> <p>I wrote about ADT Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADT\" title=\"ADT Inc.\">ADT</a></span>) previously (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723240-adt-inc-leading-player-in-us-home-security-solutions\">25<sup>th</sup> September</a>) with a buy rating, as the business is in a solid position to ride on the long-term secular tailwind for household</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/638690525/image_638690525.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741745-adt-inc-i-have-more-confidence-that-growth-can-accelerate", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 17:25:50"}, {"id": "4741753", "title": "Median Household Income In October 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448867745/image_1448867745.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Mortgage Concept\" data-id=\"1448867745\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448867745/image_1448867745.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448867745/image_1448867745.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448867745/image_1448867745.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448867745/image_1448867745.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448867745/image_1448867745.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448867745/image_1448867745.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448867745/image_1448867745.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448867745/image_1448867745.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">FatCamera/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Motio Research's initial estimate of U.S. median household income in October 2024 is $82,222. This figure is $85 (0.1%) less than the firm's initial estimate of median household income in September 2024 of <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4732025-median-household-income-in-september-2024\" rel=\"noopener\">$82,307</a>.</p> <p>Motio</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448867745/image_1448867745.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741753-median-household-income-in-october-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 17:20:00"}, {"id": "4741519", "title": "2 BDCs That Could Be The Next Stars In The Sector", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/635824660/image_635824660.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Two Gold Stars\" data-id=\"635824660\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"811px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/635824660/image_635824660.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/635824660/image_635824660.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, htt